column5: My usual question, has anyone found any coupons for the show yet (other than the recipient of TJ's kindness). Jim
I was in LeBarons yesterday and they have $2 coupons at the check-out counter.
back page of the sports section of the toronto sun has had them for a while now. theres one in todays paper cause i just clipped it out lol.
There is also one in the latest outdoor mag. Lew is right about LB's
Yup Lebaron has them and you can help yourself to all you need.
